txt.en: 'The Mirkwood spiders have only been in Cirith Ungol a short time, and yet they have already begun to destroy the forest. They suffocate and hollow out trees to use as shelter for their broodlings. The dead trees must come down.
The Mirkwood spiders have only recently arrived, but already they taint the forests in Cirith Ungol.
'We could do nothing for the trees that were already killed, but by culling the spiders, we may yet save the living forest.'
Mirkwood spiders have killed and webbed many trees in Taurlingol.\n\nYou should burn webbed trees.
Legolas can be found on a hill near Taurlingol.\n\nYou should talk to Legolas.
